<style><link href="https://drafts.csswg.org/css-contain-1/#containment-style" rel=help>

div {
  quotes: "A" "Z" "1" "9";
}
div::before{
  content: open-quote;
}

span::after {
  content: no-close-quote;
}
div::after {
  content: close-quote;
}
span {
  contain: style;
}
</style>

<p>Test passes if the text below is "AZ" (not including the quotation marks).<p>
